## Library 


Create a library system with functionality to manage items and people within the library.  


Rules:  
- At least one Abstract Class must be implemented. 							[x]
- Each item should have at least 1 additional attribute unique to itself. 	[x]
- Use of polymorphism and inheritance										[ ]
- Correct usage of access modifiers 										[x]
- Naming conventions adhered to												[x]
- Commenting only where necessary. 											[ ]


At least 3 of the following items: 
- Books 																	[x]
- Maps  																	[x]
- Government documents 														[ ]
- Media resources (Camera etc.) 											[ ]
- Newspapers 																[ ]
- Journals 																	[ ]
- Magazines 																[ ]
- Dissertations 															[x]
- Thesis 																	[ ]


ALL of the following: 
- Check out item 															[x]
- Check in item 															[x]
- Add item 																	[x]
- Remove item 																[ ]
- Update item 																[ ]
- Register person 															[-]
- Delete person 															[ ]
- Update person 															[ ]
 
Implement an ID system in your Item class, utilizing a static integer variable. 